<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="pick-on">pick on</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>挑选；故意挑剔：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Why do you pick on me to do the unpleasant jobs?
你为什么找我做这些令人不愉快的工作?</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Why pick on my family? 
为什么拿我的家庭说事？</p><footer>2011 江西</footer></div></div>